# Ping Monitor

This Python script pings a target IP and logs the status (UP/DOWN) every 5 seconds.

## How to Run:
1. Clone this repo.
2. Run `ping_monitor.py` using Python.
3. The script will log results to `ping_log.txt`.

## Example Output:

2025-02-16 14:30:00 - 8.8.8.8 is UP 2025-02-16 14:30:05 - 8.8.8.8 is UP
